  "texts": [
    "With simple prompts, GPT-4 seems to produce reappraisals that are rated better than those of humans, even when labeled as produced by GPT-4.",
    "This suggests that LLMs can be used to improve human reappraisals by suggesting edits to initial reappraisals produced by EXPLORING HUMAN AND AI EMOTIONAL SUPPORT humans (Sharma, Rushton, Lin, Nguyen, et al., 2023).",
    "High quality humans who outperform GPT-4 in their reappraisal can also be used to train language models to further improve on these domains.",
    "These studies provide a first comparison of humans and GPT-4 in reappraising negative emotional situations, but have a few important limitations that should hinder researchers from generalizing these findings.",
    "First, our study was focused on reappraisal of negative experiences and limited in length."
